text:
Thank you for the Stream Rushia, pokemon Shield brings back memories of the good old days where pokemon is everywhere.
Rushia choose a fire type starter while Polka choose a grass type starter, I wonder how well they would fight against each other.
Basically for starter pokemon, the three types are strong and weak against the types. 
Fire is effective against Grass, Grass is effective against Water, Water is effective against Fire. The starter triangle.
